Some sixth-grade students will make 50 bags of honey granola to sell at a fundraising event using the recipe shown. They will put 2 cups of granola in each bag and will sell each bag for $5.
Choose one question to answer.
Question 1: How many cups of rolled oats will the students need to buy?
Question 2: One pound of almonds costs $9.99 and has 3 cups of almonds. How much will the students need to budget for almonds?
